«DEFINE generateReadme FOR SpecificationAPI»
Hi! There are some instructions that you should follow to deploy your API.

1- Download the neccesary files, the password is 'smaproject': http://goo.gl/ngYqbd
2- In the root of your server, create a structure like "«basePath»"
3- Now, unzip te files, which were downloaded in the first step, in the folder "«basePath»"
4- Import the SQL file generated "db.sql" to your DBMS
5- Copy the PHP file generated "index.php" in the folder "«basePath»"
6- Open your browser and go to http://«host»«basePath»/index.php
«ENDDEFINE»

